<Input><Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">n := RowDimension(MDH):

q   := Vector([seq(MDH[i,4], i=1..n)]):
dq  := Vector([seq(parse(cat(&quot;dq&quot;,i)), i=1..n)]):
