<Font encoding="UTF-8">    fkall_body := cat(fkall_body, MatlabAssignMatrix(cat(&quot;Ti&quot;, i), Texp[i]), &quot;\134n&quot;):
    fkall_body := cat(fkall_body, &quot;Tlist{&quot;, i+1, &quot;} = Ti&quot;, i, &quot;;\134n&quot;);
</Font>od:

<Font encoding="UTF-8">fkall_body := cat(fkall_body, MatlabAssignMatrix(&quot;T0e&quot;, T0e_exp), &quot;\134n&quot;):
</Font>
